2812. To MARY OF HUNGARY.

Esterhazy MS. 347. Freiburg. OE. 369. 1 June 1533.

[A letter written, together with Ep. 2813, to recommend Peter Montfoert, who had brought to Erasmus at Freiburg the honorarium from the 6 States of Holland; see Ep. 2389 introd.‚ cf. Ep. 2818. 15-25.]

ERASMVS ROTERODAMVS SERENISSIMAE REGINAE MARIAE HVNGARIAE

ET BOHEMIAE VIDVAE, INFERIORIS GERMANIAE GVBERNATRICI S. D.
